6






447 Great Mall DrMilpitas, CA 95035


        (408) 273-7000
    






I like much more Eddie Bauer but my boyfriend has also a membership card of this store, so he always get me things that I love! The excuse: hey, lets check out those 20% off deals! And surely, there is always a shirt with the metallic inside that keep your super warm anywhere...and that matches with the color of my sunglasses:) Impossible not to get a good deal back home. I think they should hire a better stylist to put the clothes in a more attractive way and not so much as 'outlet display'. At least I like to buy things that are displayed in an attractive manner. This store lacks the wow factor but still has everything I want every time I go and service has always been good.







No problem.  Needed to return an online item and it was done with a smile. I was on hold for 15 minutes trying to see if the Columbia outlet near where I live would take it, since I was returning Sorel shoes.  I hung up because 15 minutes is too long to wait for an answer. Here they were pleasant, took it and give me my money back. It's a large store with a big selection. I would definitely come here to shop if I didn't have the friends and family discount, which always makes it cheaper for me to shop online but I don't want to pay return shipping if it doesn't work out.







I have never been so upset with a company.  I live in the desert and I bought a coat to go to Buffalo in January.  I purchased the coat on January 7 and paid extra for 2 day shipping.  It is now 10 days later and the coat has not arrived.  I was told by Customer Care that there was a snow storm that delayed my coat.  I was not informed of the delay and missed my chance to buy another coat   I don't have enough balance on my card to purchase another coat and I'm cold.  AWFUL!!!!!!!







They close at 9 and we were there 8:53 to pay for a jacket we decided and they didn't let us in. Bad customer service and not follow the operation time. Lazy employee....







Employee Norman has great customer service. He honored and did a price adjustment since one of the jackets wasn't coming up 50% but there was a sign that said 50% off - didn't give me any hassle and was kind and friendly.







I had a horrible experience here when I tried to do an exchange last week .There was  one rude  guy in the counter doing all the return.He constantly kept complaining about customers trying to do return to the other guy in the counter infront of the other customers .We went for an exchange , the guy turned us away after half  hour wait ,even though we had all the receipts and tags .Keep off from this store and take your business elsewhere unless you like to be yelled at.







            Columbia Sportswear
        






