        7/1/2017
    








1 check-in
        


We are fans of Columbia Sportswear Company.  This branch at the San Francisco Premium Outlet mall in Livermore, CA is no exception.It is one of the larger stores that we have patronized.  More inventory choices makes for greater selection.  Store was well organized and clean.  Staff was helpful and answered our questions.  We scored some terrific deals at their Clearance sections!Recommend checking out this Columbia store for your sportswear needs.




































