        1/2/2017
    

Leah the supervisor in charge today was INCREDIBLY RUDE to me. She displayed a total lack of customer service concerning my return. I understand your "policy," but you DO NOT address customers in the cold and unprofessional way that she did to me. I was simply asking for STORE CREDIT for an item purchased 20 days ago with which I have A RECEIPT AND THE CREDIT CARD USED FOR THE PURCHASE. She was incredibly cold and told me t go ahead and call her corporate office to complain.DO NOT BUY ANYTHING IN THIS STORE or AT ANY COLUMBIA STORE, OR THAT MATTER. REI had the best return policy and sells Columbia items. They don't treat their customers like thieves and deviants EVER.




