        8/23/2015
    








1 check-in
        


The workers here are very friendly and helpful. I was looking for a winter jacket but since Im always cold it would be an everyday jacket. I been eyeing this jacket for 2 months but decided to wait since it was still summer, but with the approach of winter coming a long and the announcement of 30 new stores I have decided to hit this outlet up again. I still don't agree with the name of this outlet as I don't think it would draw more people in let alone tourists. But I am glad I went on a whim with my friend and made a day out of it. They had a good sale at this time 25% off additionally. The jacket I wanted was priced at $169.99 with an additional 25% off it came down to $130 before taxes but at checkout it rang for $90!!!!   The cashier told me it was on sale because it was last year's style. SCORE!The customer service here is superb. I asked for 2 different sizes and they were happy to assist me. Everyone I encountered was very friendly and accommodating and because of this I will always return!




