Pretty good selection of ski jackets when I went. I found a great deal on the jacket and ski pants I purchased. I also found a couple of other sweaters I liked for my weekend in the snow that were marked down. I signed up for their rewards program online the night before, and they were nice enough to honor the 10% discount (only valid in-store). The staff was friendly and helpful. I liked this store and plan to come back next time I need some more gear.




