        2/8/2013
    








1 check-in
        







First to Review
        


The best place to shop for outerwear in the East Bay.Columbia Sportswear has super awesome technology meant to withstand all sorts of weather.The people who work here are knowledgeable and friendly.The prices are spectacular. I got a pair of SOREL boots for really cheap. Their clearance shoe table is always stocked.In my opinion, Columbia is waaay better than Northface and the garments last that much longer.With a new location out in the Tri-Valley, hikers, runners, and skiers alike will definitely find something for themselves.




