        10/26/2013
    








1 check-in
        









            Listed in Yelp 100 Challenge, Go out and shopify!


Do you need sporty clothes?  How about outdoors clothes?  Then you should go to the Columbia outlet.  They had a good selection of new things and helpful people. The clothes were laid out like any store, nicely on racks.  The selection seemed very similar to what I would find at REI or otherwise, regular in season, normal clothes with a variety of sizes, at a significant discount.I was asked if I needed help a few times.  They ended up starting a room in the fitting area for me and even brought other sizes when the clothes I had didn't fit. Of course I think the ratio of staff to guests was close to 1:1 when I went so they should pay attention!




