        8/14/2013
    








1 check-in
        


Came here during a 4th of July weekend sale and this place was crazy! Tons of good deals, but it was hard to find your size since there were sooo many people around. The store was clean, but with lots of people = messy store. The line to the dressing room was ridiculously long, but people moved in an orderly fashion.Overall,  I found great hiking pants and a sweater here all for less than $80. Great quality and good deals during an event. I would recommend shopping here  if you are at the outlets. Friendly staff and good lighting.




