Columbia Sportswear

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Columbia Sportswear Company





Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: COLM


Industry
Apparel


Founded
1938; 79 years ago (1938)


Headquarters
Washington County, Oregon (near Beaverton),
United States
45°31′46″N 122°49′31″W﻿ / ﻿45.52938°N 122.82535°W﻿ / 45.52938; -122.82535Coordinates: 45°31′46″N 122°49′31″W﻿ / ﻿45.52938°N 122.82535°W﻿ / 45.52938; -122.82535



