t me the notes).  The notes said that they found the mittens (outside of the box), and the jacket was never found.  The jacket was marked stolen, and the mittens were shipped back to C.  You know what I was told at this point???!!!!  I had to wait for the mittens to arrive back to C!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!!  I cant even tell you how livid I was!  Why do I have to wait for them to get the mittens back whne the invest. was closed and completed.  I finally got my money back a month after I ordered.  Thanks Columbia!  You lost a great customer.  Thanks but no thanks for the offer of 20% off an order.  You are all heart!!!!




