Best Sports Wear in Portland











Mosaic









List




















1.         Portland Running Company








            54 reviews
    










                        No pressure to buy, they care about what's right for your needs.
                














2.         Fleet Feet Sports








            112 reviews
    










                        They do gait analysis and provide a few options.
                














3.         The Leotard








            35 reviews
    










                        The best dance supply store in Portland!
                














4.         US Outdoor Store








            88 reviews
    










                        They have the snowboarding/ski equipment, brand names AND the sale annex.
                
















5.         Next Adventure








            193 reviews
    










                        They also have some great deals in the bargain basement..
                














6.         Columbia Sportswear Outlet








            49 reviews
    










                        I've been living in Portland for almost two years and I still don't have a waterproof jacket.
                














7.         Athletes Lounge








            23 reviews
    










                        My first experience was renting a wetsuit for my first race in 2012.
                














8.         Foot Traffic Sellwood








            11 reviews
    










                        Great selection of running gear , shoes and fuel ( gels etc ).
                











