        4/8/2017
    

I've tried using their unsubscribe form many times, but it does not work (probably because it thinks email addresses can't have a plus sign in them). Then, I opened 5 support tickets over the course of 2 months. Each time they told me they unsubscribed me, yet I still receive email from them.I regret giving them my email, but I do not regret buying a jacket from them. It's one of my daily drivers.




