        2/16/2017
            





Updated review



My review is regarding Customer Service after placing an online order. I question the speed of delivery order and after two full weeks still no package.  I tied to trace it but it may no sense... Coming to California (on the west coast) package was in Chicago for several days.  When I question the 'Customer Care' rep I was told delivery is between 8-13 days.  I told her that was not what my email shipping notice informed me of.  I was basically told I had to wait! Still waiting package was now in Iowa again I'm on west coast as the company is too. After several rude email from 'Customer Care' rep I was still left with no answers or package.  So I went to the mall and purchase another Mother's Day gift. Finally after two PLUS weeks package arrived I know one reason it took so long the box was re-re-recycled and previous labels were not removed. Now at checkout I did NOT check box to recycle box.   Ask to speak with Supervisor still waiting all I received was another rude email for 'Customer Care' more like Customer careLESS rep.  I really love Columbia clothing but I will look for another company.




