        11/30/2016
    

Lifetime warranty unless it's classified as a sportswear item, then it only has a one year warranty. So if the zipper stop falls off and so does the zipper make sure it happens within 364 days. Stuff happens, but then the company should step up and fix. Oh, I could mail back and they would evaluate and let me know, but probably not. On a small positive note, I did receive a quick and professional response to my email. But that didn't help fix my wife's jacket. Not satisfied.




