        10/31/2014
    

I am flabbergasted by some of the bad reviews posted here.  Columbia sportswear has consistently been a winner for me.  I love that they offer good quality, REAL sportswear in plus sizes for women.  Their clothing is good quality, well fitting and BEAUTIFUL!  I don't live in an area with a Columbia store, so I order online.  Even so, I have never purchased a product from this website that I needed to return.  And every single time I wear a Columbia garment, I get scads of comments and compliments from folks who want to know where I buy my clothes.  The last time i purchased a shirt from Columbia, my husband told me that I looked beautiful and said I should get one in each color they offered!  As a plus sized woman, I have often felt victimized by companies who cater to people with hard-to-fit bodies;  charging premium prices for poor quality goods, simply because our choices are scarce.  I cannot express how much I appreciate a mainline business who makes quality garments in all sizes and treats their larger sized customers exactly the same as their smaller counterparts.  When I wear Columbia, I feel comfortable, beautiful and dressed appropriately for the Rocky Mountain region where I live.  I heartily recommend Columbia!




